# Mobile (Expo → native App Store)

- Router: `apps/mobile/app/` (Expo Router). Auth → onboarding birth → `(tabs)`
- Tema: `constants/theme.ts` + `components/ui.tsx` (Syne / Manrope fontlar)
- API: yalnızca `lib/api.ts` üzerinden; base URL `lib/config.ts`
- **App Store:** `EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_ENV=production` + HTTPS `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` (EAS secret). LAN/Metro yok.
- **Yerel native test:** `development` + LAN IP → `npm run ios:prebuild` → Xcode ⌘R
- Auth state: `lib/auth.tsx` + `lib/storage.ts` (SecureStore / AsyncStorage)
- Doğum formu: `components/BirthForm.tsx` + `searchWorldCities` (@asto/shared)
- Monetizasyon stub: `lib/monetization.ts`
- Ortam: `app.config.js` + `EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_ENV` / `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL`
- Native plugin: `plugins/withNativeIosStandalone.js` (gömülü bundle, Metro asla)
- Dağıtım: `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md`
- `@asto/shared` import et; sabitleri mobile içinde tekrar tanımlama
